These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, siglo, dannemann, swisher, alhambra, game, tiparillo
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: february, march, august, november, june, december, september
 1. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is the swisher-smoker##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the dannemann-smoker is in the middle##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1
 7. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
11. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Cigar           | alhambra | swisher | siglo | dannemann | blend | game | tiparillo |
| Birthday   | february    | june   | november      | december | august    | march    | september         |

