.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: ship, quad-bike, van, helicopter, train, motorbike, skateboard
The people have 7 different hobbies: camping, hiking, board-games, photography, gardening, writing, video-games
 1. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person who's hobby is gardening is in the middle##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 9. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person driving the van##1
10. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Transport          | ship | quad-bike | train | helicopter | motorbike | skateboard | van |
| Hobby   | hiking      | board-games   | photography   | gardening      | camping       | video-games       | writing     |

