.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
House: cottage, cape-cod, colonial, palace, gothic-revival, ranch-style, futuristic
7 different pets are kept: rat, goat, goldfish, hamster, horse, chinchilla, bird
 1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 3. the owner of the goat is on the left of the futuristic house##1
 4. the cottage house is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 5. the owner of the rat is the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
 7. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the ranch-style house is the owner of the hamster##1
10. the colonial house is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
11. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
12. the futuristic house is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| House   | cape-cod | gothic-revival     | colonial  | ranch-style       | cottage       | futuristic  | palace   |
| Pet    | chinchilla  | rat | bird | hamster | goat | goldfish | horse |

