 6. the victorian house is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the victorian house##1
 8. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the cape-cod house is the person who growsorchid##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the wooden house##1
11. the person who growsbegonia is the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
