 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |     5      |     6      |    7     |
| Birthday   | march    | september    | may   | july | february | june | january   |
